OL,3,CTourists in Thailand jump into sea as
OL,4,Cflames rip through ferry
OL,6,FPassengers jump into the water away
OL,7,Ffrom flames tearing through a boat in
OL,8,Fthe Gulf of Thailand
OL,10,FTourists were forced to jump into the
OL,11,Fsea to escape flames ripping through a
OL,12,Fferry in the Gulf of Thailand on
OL,13,FThursday morning.
OL,15,FThe overnight ferry from Surat Thani
OL,16,Fprovince was about to arrive at Koh
OL,17,FTao, a popular tourist destination off
OL,18,Fthe Thai coast, when one of the
OL,19,Fpassengers reported hearing a
OL,20,Fcrackling sound and said they could
OL,21,Fsmell smoke.
