OL,3,CTourists in Thailand jump into sea as
OL,4,Cflames rip through ferry
OL,6,FMaitree Promjampa, a Surat Thani
OL,7,Fresident who often travels to Koh Tao
OL,8,Ffor work, said he saw billowing smoke
OL,9,Fand fire less than five minutes later,
OL,10,Fwhen people started shouting and rang
OL,11,Fthe alarm.
OL,13,F"We could barely get the life vests in
OL,14,Ftime," he told The Associated Press.
OL,15,F"It was chaotic. People were weeping
OL,16,F... I also teared up."
