OL,3,CTourists in Thailand jump into sea as
OL,4,Cflames rip through ferry
OL,6,FVideos showed people hurrying out of
OL,7,Fthe ferry's cabin while putting on
OL,8,Flife vests, as thick black smoke swept
OL,9,Facross the vessel, which was later
OL,10,Fengulfed in flames.
OL,12,FAll 108 people on board the ship were
OL,13,Frescued - 97 of them were passengers,
OL,14,FSurat Thani officials said on Facebook.
OL,16,FMr Promjampa said several boats came
OL,17,Fto their rescue around 20 minutes
OL,18,Fafter they called for help.
