OL,3,CTourists in Thailand jump into sea as
OL,4,Cflames rip through ferry
OL,6,FBut the rescue boats could not get
OL,7,Fclose to the ferry out of fear of
OL,8,Fexplosions and people had to jump into
OL,9,Fthe sea to be rescued, he said.
OL,11,F"Everyone had to help themselves," Mr
OL,12,FPromjampa added.
OL,14,FVideos showed the ferry, which did not
OL,15,Fsink despite the damage, was also
OL,16,Fcarrying several vehicles.
OL,18,FOfficials said the fire has been
OL,19,Fbrought under control and confirmed it
OL,20,Fhad originated in the engine, but the
OL,21,Fcause is being investigated.
